Interface Finalizable

All Known Implementing Classes:
DataAU
public interface Finalizable

Interface Finalizable must implemented by classes that have clean up functionality.
In some cases object that have running threads inside could not be finalized. This interface tells that object must be forcedly finalized before all references to the one are lost.
